    "policies": {
      "prefix": "Policy ",
      "privacy": {
        "title": "Privacy Policy",
        "content": "CUSTOMER INFORMATION PRIVACY POLICY\n\n1. Purpose of Information Collection\nFShop collects customer information for the following purposes:\n• Process orders and deliver to customer-requested addresses\n• Provide information about products, services, and promotional programs\n• Support customers with questions or complaints\n• Improve service quality and shopping experience\n\n2. Scope of Collection\nWe collect personal information when customers:\n• Register an account on the website\n• Place orders and make payments\n• Contact customer service department\n\n3. Privacy Commitment\n• Do not share, sell, or rent personal information to third parties\n• Apply advanced security measures to protect data\n• Only authorized staff have access to customer information\n• Strictly comply with legal regulations on personal data protection"
      },
      "warranty": {
        "title": "Warranty Policy",
        "content": "PRODUCT WARRANTY POLICY\n\n1. Warranty Period\n• Genuine phones: Varies by product line\n• Genuine accessories: 6-12 months depending on product type\n• Batteries and chargers: 6 months\n\n2. Warranty Conditions\n• Product is still within warranty period\n• Warranty seal and warranty card are intact\n• Defects from manufacturer, not from user\n\n3. Non-Warranty Cases\n• Product has expired warranty\n• Damage from impact, drop, water ingress\n• Unauthorized disassembly or external repair\n• Incorrect use or installation of non-genuine software\n\n4. Warranty Process\n• Step 1: Create warranty request on website from order\n• Step 2: Wait for confirmation from warranty department\n• Step 3: Receive warranty appointment and bring product to store\n• Step 4: Product inspection and warranty\n• Step 5: Return product to customer"
      },
      "shipping": {
        "title": "Shipping Policy",
        "content": "SHIPPING POLICY\n\n1. Shipping Scope\n• Nationwide shipping through reputable carriers\n• Da Nang inner city: Same-day delivery\n• Other provinces: 2-5 business days\n\n2. Shipping Fees\n• Free shipping for orders from 2,000,000 VND\n• Da Nang inner city: Free\n• Nearby districts: 30,000 VND\n• Other provinces: According to shipping rate table\n\n3. Payment Methods\n• Cash on delivery (COD)\n• Bank transfer\n• Payment via VNPay e-wallet\n\n4. Product Inspection on Receipt\n• Customers have the right to inspect products before payment\n• Record unboxing video as evidence if there are issues\n• Refuse delivery if product is incorrect or damaged"
      }
    }
